name: BOLSO BOX TOTE ALBION
campo_tres:
Box tote con detalles en tonos dorados, cierre con cremallera, asa desmontable, bolsillo interior y colgante dorado "Go Bananas".

Ancho: 18 cm

campo_seis:
Mini box tote featuring gold tone hardware, a zipper along the top, an adjustable, removable shoulder strap, an inside slip pocket and "Go Bananas" charm.

This item comes with a dust bag.
